title: Pakistan vs England: 1st Test, Day 2 - Alastair Cook, Moeen Ali batted sensibly after Shoaib Malik hits double century
text: Openers Alastair Cook and Moeen Ali batted solidly to take England to 56-0 after Shoaib Malik's double century lifted Pakistan to a mammoth total in the first Test in Abu Dhabi on Wedensday. Â»
